{"type":null,"faqId":44800,"title":"为什么屏幕突然缩小，无法满屏显示？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{text-indent:0.29166666in;margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:0.29166666in;margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:0.29166666in;margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">手势左右滑动导航栏区域，可以触发单手屏幕功能，方便单手操作手机，操作路径：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">“设置 &gt; 全部设置 &gt; 智能辅助 &gt; 单手操作 &gt; 单手屏幕”，关闭即可。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=161775\" style=\"width:2.3368056in;height:3.9361112in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=161776\" style=\"width:2.2395833in;height:3.9375in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=161777\" style=\"width:2.25in;height:3.9979167in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>* 图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"301","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442409263000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":7,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":